title Luồng 1 - Class (Dashboard)

class AdminDashboardController {
  +doGet(req, res)
}
class RestaurantAnalyticsDAO {
  +countAllRestaurants()
  +countRestaurantsByStatus(status)
  +getTotalOrdersAllRestaurants()
  +getTotalRevenueAllRestaurants()
  +getTopRestaurantsByRevenue(limit)
}
class RestaurantAnalytics
class User

AdminDashboardController ..> User : reads session
AdminDashboardController ..> RestaurantAnalyticsDAO
RestaurantAnalyticsDAO ..> RestaurantAnalytics : returns List

newpage
title Luồng 2 - Class (System report)

class AdminSystemReportController {
